# Monorepo env guidance (do not store subapp secrets here by default)
#
# This repository contains multiple apps with different env scopes.
# Put secrets in the closest app folder instead of repo root.
#
# Use these files instead:
# - shimeji-xlm/.env                -> Stellar deploy/contracts/IPFS seed secrets
# - shimeji-xlm/nextjs/.env.local   -> Stellar web app (Prisma/API/UI) secrets
# - shimeji-eth/.../.env*           -> Ethereum app envs (see that subproject)
#
# Root-level envs should only be used if a root script explicitly documents it.
